title: NO LAUNCH BUTTON!
body: Lately whenever I have been opening League up its not coming up with a Launch button just the blue screen...Someone Please HELP ME!

replies.body:
Hey Woljin,

If you're not seeing the Launch button, it's likely there's a connection issue between your client and the League of Legends servers. Please ensure that League of Legends is added as an exception to any antivirus applications and firewalls that you may have running.
